  <SourceScript>k__BackingField: 'IGM: Hey so. A buddy got in an adventuring accident.
    Larrrrge skull fracture.


    IGM: Gonna need something... probably medicine-y?


    IGM:
    Probably related to like. Healing headaches too.


    IGM: A skull fracture
    is the biggest headache you can have right?


    IGM: Just mix a headache potion
    with something medicine-y.'
